"          <li>For other purposes: We may use Your information for other purposes, such as data analysis, identifying usage trends, determining the effectiveness of our promotional campaigns, and evaluating and improving our Service, products, services, marketing, and your experience.</li>\n"
"        </ol>We may share Your personal information in the following situations:<ol class=\"list-disc my-2\">\n"
"          <li>With Service Providers: We may share Your personal information with Service Providers to monitor and analyze the use of our Service, and to contact You.</li>\n"
"          <li>For business transfers: We may share or transfer Your personal information in connection with, or during negotiations of, any merger, sale of Company assets, financing, or acquisition of all or a portion of Our business to another company.</li>\n"
"          <li>With Affiliates: We may share Your information with Our affiliates, in which case we will require those affiliates to honor this Privacy Policy. Affiliates include Our parent company and any other subsidiaries, joint venture partners, or other companies that We control or that are under common control with Us.</li>\n"
"          <li>With business partners: We may share Your information with Our business partners to offer You certain products, services, or promotions.</li>\n"
"          <li>With other users: when You share personal information or otherwise interact in the public areas with other users, such information may be viewed by all users and may be publicly distributed outside.</li>\n"
"          <li>With Your consent: We may disclose Your personal information for any other purpose with Your consent.</li>\n"
"        </ol>We may also share your Personal Information and other information in special cases if we have a good reason to believe that it is necessary to: (i) comply with law, regulation, request by an applicable authority or court order; (ii) detect, prevent or otherwise address fraud, security, violation of our policies or technical issues; (iii) enforce the provisions of this Privacy Policy or any other agreements between you and IsAlgo, including investigation of potential violations thereof; or (iv) protect against harm to the rights, property or safety of the Company, its partners, its affiliates, users, or the public.\n"
"\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Retention of Your Personal Data</h3>\n"
"        The Company will retain Your Personal Data only for as long as is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy. We will retain and use Your Personal Data to the extent necessary to comply with our legal obligations (for example, if we are required to retain your data to comply with applicable laws), resolve disputes, and enforce our legal agreements and policies.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        The Company will also retain Usage Data for internal analysis purposes. Usage Data is generally retained for a shorter period of time, except when this data is used to strengthen the security or to improve the functionality of Our Service, or We are legally obligated to retain this data for longer time periods.\n"
"\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Transfer of Your Personal Data</h3>\n"
"        Your information, including Personal Data, is processed at the Company’s operating offices and in any other places where the parties involved in the processing are located. It means that this information may be transferred to, and maintained on, computers located outside of Your state, province, country, or other governmental jurisdiction where the data protection laws may differ from those of Your jurisdiction.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        Your consent to this Privacy Policy followed by Your submission of such information represents Your agreement to that transfer.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        The Company will take all steps reasonably necessary to ensure that Your data is treated securely and in accordance with this Privacy Policy and no transfer of Your Personal Data will take place to an organization or a country unless there are adequate controls in place including the security of Your data and other personal information.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        Any processing performed by any of our third-party service providers (“Recipients”) will, where required by law, be governed by a data processing agreement in the form required by law, preserving any and all of your statutory data protection rights and obligating the Recipients to respect the Personal Information and handle it in accordance with the relevant laws. If a Recipient is located outside the EEA, we will transfer your data only to such countries as approved by the European Commission as providing an adequate level of data protection, or ensure that the legal agreements governing the data transfer provide an adequate level of data protection. The Recipients are required to maintain the confidentiality of such information and to use your Personal Information only in the course of providing the aforementioned services and only for the purposes that %(site_url)s dictates.\n"
"\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Delete Your Personal Data</h3>\n"
"        You have the right to delete or request that We assist in deleting the Personal Data that We have collected about You.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        Our Service may give You the ability to delete certain information about You from within the Service.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        You may update, amend, or delete Your information at any time by signing in to Your Account, if you have one, and visiting the account settings section that allows you to manage Your personal information. You may also contact Us to request access to, correct, or delete any personal information that You have provided to Us.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        Please note, however, that We may need to retain certain information when we have a legal obligation or lawful basis to do so.\n"
"\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Disclosure of Your Personal Data</h3>\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Business Transactions</h3>\n"
"        If the Company is involved in a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, Your Personal Data may be transferred. We will provide notice before Your Personal Data is transferred and becomes subject to a different Privacy Policy.\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Law Enforcement</h3>\n"
"        Under certain circumstances, the Company may be required to disclose Your Personal Data if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities (e.g., a court or a government agency).\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Other Legal Requirements</h3>\n"
"        The Company may disclose Your Personal Data in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to:<ol class=\"list-disc my-2\">\n"
"          <li>Comply with a legal obligation</li>\n"
"          <li>Protect and defend the rights or property of the Company</li>\n"
"          <li>Prevent or investigate possible wrongdoing in connection with the Service</li>\n"
"          <li>Protect the personal safety of Users of the Service or the public</li>\n"
"          <li>Protect against legal liability</li>\n"
"        </ol>\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Security of Your Personal Data</h3>\n"
"        We use reasonable efforts to safeguard the integrity, availability, and confidentiality of all personal data that we process relating to you and regularly review and enhance our technical, physical, and managerial procedures to ensure that your personal data is protected from:<ol class=\"list-disc my-2\">\n"
"          <li>Unauthorized access;</li>\n"
"          <li>Improper use or disclosure;</li>\n"
"          <li>Unauthorized modification;</li>\n"
"          <li>Unlawful destruction or accidental loss.</li>\n"
"        </ol>To this end, we have implemented security policies, rules, and technical measures to protect the personal data that we have under our control. All our employees and data processors, who have access to and are associated with the processing of personal data, are further obliged to respect the confidentiality of our clients’ and visitors’ personal data.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        By its very nature, however, the Internet is not a secure medium and data sent via this medium can potentially be subject to unauthorized acts by third parties. We cannot guarantee the privacy or confidentiality of any information passing over our website.\n"
"        <br /><br />\n"
"        Moreover, data sent via the Internet may be transmitted across international borders even where the sender and receiver of information are located in the same country. Consequently, data relating to you may be transmitted via a country having a lower level of data protection than that existing in your country of residence. We shall accept no responsibility or liability whatsoever for the security of your data while in transit through the Internet."

msgid "Your Legal Rights"
msgstr "您的合法权利"

msgid ""
"You have rights we need to make you aware of. The rights available to you "
"depend on our reason for processing your personal data. If you need more "
"detailed information or wish to exercise any of the rights set out below, "
"please contact us."
msgstr "您拥有我们需要让您了解的权利。您可获得的权利取决于我们处理您个人数据的原因。如果您需要更多详细信息或希望行使下列任何权利，请联系我们。"

msgid ""
"You may:<ol class=\"list-disc my-2\">\n"
"          <li>Request access to your personal data, which enables you to obtain confirmation of whether we are processing your personal data, to receive a copy of the personal data we hold about you and information regarding how your personal data is being used by us;</li>\n"
"          <li>Request rectification of your personal data by asking us to rectify information you think is inaccurate and to complete information you think is incomplete, though we may need to verify the accuracy of the new data you provide to us;</li>\n"
"          <li>Request erasure of your personal data by asking us to delete or remove personal data we hold about you; note, however, that we may not always be able to comply with your request for erasure for specific legal reasons which will be notified to you;</li>\n"
"          <li>Object to the processing of your personal data, where we are relying on a legitimate interest (or those of a third party) and there is something about your particular situation which makes you want to object to processing on this ground as you feel it impacts on your fundamental rights and freedoms; in some cases, we may demonstrate that we have compelling legitimate grounds to process your information which override your rights and freedoms; you also have the right to object where we are processing your personal data for direct marketing purposes;</li>\n"
"          <li>Require that decisions be reconsidered if they are made solely by automated means, without human involvement; we use automated tools to make sure that you are eligible to be our customer taking into account our interests and legal obligations; if these automated tools indicate that you do not meet our acceptance criteria, we will not onboard you as our customer;</li>\n"
"          <li>Request restriction of processing your personal data, which enables you to ask us to suspend the processing of your personal data, if you want us to establish the data accuracy; where our use of the data is unlawful, but you do not want us to erase it; where you need us to hold the data even if we no longer require it as you need it to establish, exercise or defend legal claims, or if you have objected to our use of your data, but we need to verify whether we have overriding legitimate grounds to use it;</li>\n"
"          <li>Request the transfer of your personal data to you or to a third party, and we will provide to you, or a third party you have chosen (where technically feasible), your personal data in a structured, commonly used, machine-readable format; note that this right only applies to automated information which you initially provided consent for us to use or where we used the information to perform a contract with you;</li>\n"
"          <li>Withdraw consent at any time where we are relying on consent to process your personal data; however, this will not affect the lawfulness of any processing carried out before you withdraw your consent; if you withdraw your consent, we may not be able to provide certain products or services to you, but we will advise you if this is the case at the time you withdraw your consent;</li>\n"
"          <li>Complain to the relevant authority about any perceived violation and to seek compensation for damages in the courts.</li>\n"
"        </ol>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"您可以：<ol class=\"list-disc my-2\">\n"
"          <li>请求访问您的个人数据，以便您能够确认我们是否正在处理您的个人数据、接收我们持有的有关您的个人数据的副本以及有关我们如何使用您的个人数据的信息；</li>\n"
"          <li>要求我们更正您认为不准确的信息并补充您认为不完整的信息，以请求更正您的个人数据，但我们可能需要验证您向我们提供的新数据的准确性；</li>\n"
"          <li>通过要求我们删除我们持有的有关您的个人数据来请求删除您的个人数据；但请注意，由于特定的法律原因，我们可能并不总是能够满足您的删除请求，具体法律原因将通知您；</li>\n"
"          <li>反对处理您的个人数据，因为我们依赖合法利益（或第三方的利益），并且您的特殊情况使您想要反对基于此的处理，因为您认为这会影响您的基本权利和自由；在某些情况下，我们可能会证明我们有令人信服的合法理由来处理您的信息，这会凌驾于您的权利和自由之上；您还有权反对我们出于直接营销目的处理您的个人数据；</li>\n"
"          <li>如果决策仅通过自动化方式做出，没有人工参与，则要求重新考虑；我们使用自动化工具来确保您有资格成为我们的客户，同时考虑到我们的利益和法律义务；如果这些自动化工具表明您不符合我们的接受标准，我们将不会让您成为我们的客户；</li>\n"
"          <li>请求限制处理您的个人数据，如果您希望我们确定数据的准确性，您可以要求我们暂停处理您的个人数据；我们对数据的使用是非法的，但您不希望我们删除它；您需要我们保留数据，即使我们不再需要它，因为您需要它来建立、行使或捍卫法律索赔，或者如果您反对我们使用您的数据，但我们需要验证我们是否有压倒性的合法理由来使用它；</li>\n"
"          <li>请求将您的个人数据传输给您或第三方，我们将以结构化、常用、机器可读的格式向您或您选择的第三方（在技术上可行的情况下）提供您的个人数据；请注意，此权利仅适用于您最初同意我们使用的自动信息，或者我们使用该信息来履行与您签订的合同的情况；</li>\n"
"          <li>如果我们依赖您的同意来处理您的个人数据，请随时撤回同意；但是，这不会影响您撤回同意之前进行的任何处理的合法性；如果您撤回同意，我们可能无法向您提供某些产品或服务，但如果您撤回同意时出现这种情况，我们会通知您；</li>\n"
"          <li>就任何发现的违规行为向相关机构提出投诉，并向法院寻求损害赔偿。</li>\n"
"        </ol>"

msgid "Children’s Privacy"
msgstr "儿童隐私"

msgid ""
"Our Service does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly"
" collect personally identifiable information from anyone under the age of "
"13. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has "
"provided Us with Personal Data, please contact Us. If We become aware that "
"We have collected Personal Data from anyone under the age of 13 without "
"verification of parental consent, We take steps to remove that information "
"from Our servers.<br /><br />If We need to rely on consent as a legal basis "
"for processing Your information and Your country requires consent from a "
"parent, We may require Your parent’s consent before We collect and use that "
"information."
msgstr ""
"我们的服务不针对 13 岁以下的任何人。我们不会故意收集 13 "
"岁以下的任何人的个人身份信息。如果您是父母或监护人，并且您知道您的孩子向我们提供了个人数据，请与我们联系。如果我们发现我们在未经父母同意的情况下收集了 "
"13 岁以下任何人的个人数据，我们会采取措施从我们的服务器中删除该信息。<br /><br "
"/>如果我们需要依赖同意作为处理您的信息的法律依据，并且您所在的国家/地区需要父母的同意，我们可能会在收集和使用该信息之前要求您父母的同意。"

msgid "Links to Other Websites"
msgstr "其他网站的链接"

msgid ""
"Our Service may contain links to other websites that are not operated by Us."
" If You click on a third-party link, You will be directed to that third "
"party’s site. We strongly advise You to review the Privacy Policy of every "
"site You visit.<br /><br />We have no control over and assume no "
"responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-"
"party sites or services."
msgstr ""
"我们的服务可能包含指向非我们运营的其他网站的链接。如果您点击第三方链接，您将被定向到该第三方的网站。我们强烈建议您查看您访问的每个网站的隐私政策。<br"
" /><br />我们无法控制任何第三方网站或服务的内容、隐私政策或做法，也不承担任何责任。"

msgid "Changes to this Privacy Policy"
msgstr "本隐私政策的变更"

msgid ""
"We may update Our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify You of "
"any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.<br /><br />We "
"will let You know via email and/or a prominent notice on Our Service, prior "
"to the change becoming effective and update the “Last updated” date at the "
"top of this Privacy Policy.<br /><br />You are advised to review this "
"Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy "
"are effective when they are posted on this page."
msgstr ""
"我们可能会不时更新我们的隐私政策。我们将通过在此页面上发布新的隐私政策来通知您任何变更。<br /><br "
"/>在变更生效之前，我们将通过电子邮件和/或我们服务上的显着通知告知您，并更新本隐私政策顶部的“最后更新”日期。<br /><br "
"/>建议您定期查看本隐私政策以了解任何变更。本隐私政策的更改在发布到本页面后即生效。"

msgid "Governing Law and Jurisdiction"
msgstr "适用法律和管辖权"

msgid ""
"This agreement and any dispute or claim (including non-contractual disputes "
"or claims) arising out of or in connection with it or its subject matter or "
"formation shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of "
"Florida, US."
msgstr "本协议以及因本协议或其标的物或形成而产生或与之相关的任何争议或索赔（包括非合同争议或索赔）均应受美国佛罗里达州法律管辖并按其解释。"

msgid "Data Controller"
msgstr "数据控制者"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(site_url)s is the controller of your personal information. The contact "
"person for data protection-related matters is %(support_email)s."
msgstr "%(site_url)s 是您个人信息的控制者。数据保护相关事宜的联系人是 %(support_email)s。"

msgid "Contact Us"
msgstr "联系我们"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, You can contact us by "
"email: %(support_email)s"
msgstr "如果您对本隐私政策有任何疑问，您可以通过电子邮件联系我们：%(support_email)s"

msgid "IsAlgo | Frequently Asked Questions About IsAlgo"
msgstr "IsAlgo |关于 IsAlgo 的常见问题"

msgid "These are some of the frequently asked questions:"
msgstr "以下是一些常见问题："

msgid "What is IsAlgo?"
msgstr "什么是 IsAlgo？"

msgid ""
"IsAlgo is a platform that provides advanced trading strategies built for "
"TradingView. Our strategies are backtestable, automatable, and work across "
"any market — crypto, forex, stocks — and any timeframe. Whether you're a "
"beginner or a pro, our tools are designed to help you trade smarter."
msgstr ""
"IsAlgo 是一个为 TradingView "
"构建的提供高级交易策略的平台。我们的策略是可回测的、可自动化的，并且适用于任何市场（加密货币、外汇、股票）和任何时间范围。无论您是初学者还是专业人士，我们的工具都旨在帮助您更智能地进行交易。"

msgid "What do I need to get started?"
msgstr "我需要什么才能开始？"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"All you need is a <a class=\"underline\" href=\"%(tv_link)s\" "
"target=\"_blank\">TradingView account</a> and basic trading knowledge. Once "
"you sign up on IsAlgo and choose a plan, you will enter your TradingView "
"username and gain instant access to all the strategies included in your "
"plan."
msgstr ""
"您所需要的只是一个<a class=\"underline\" href=\"%(tv_link)s\" "
"target=\"_blank\">TradingView 帐户</a>和基本交易知识。一旦您注册 IsAlgo 并选择一个计划，您将输入您的 "
"TradingView 用户名并立即访问您的计划中包含的所有策略。"

msgid "How do I access the strategies?"
msgstr "我如何访问这些策略？"

msgid ""
"After subscribing, go to your settings and enter your TradingView username. "
"We'll guide you on where to find it. Once submitted, all strategies included"
" in your plan are automatically added to your TradingView account and ready "
"to use."
msgstr ""
"订阅后，转到您的设置并输入您的 TradingView 用户名。我们将指导您在哪里可以找到它。提交后，您计划中包含的所有策略都会自动添加到您的 "
"TradingView 账户中并可供使用。"

msgid "What are the different strategy types?"
msgstr "有哪些不同的策略类型？"

msgid ""
"<strong>Free</strong> — available to all registered users, no subscription "
"needed.<br /><strong>Premium</strong> — requires an active Monthly or Yearly"
" subscription.<br /><strong>Elite</strong> — exclusive to Lifetime members "
"only.<br /><strong>Exclusive</strong> — created by independent traders and "
"published on our platform. These are not included in any membership and must"
" be purchased separately from their authors."
msgstr ""
"<strong>免费</strong> - 可供所有注册用户使用，无需订阅。<br /><strong>高级版</strong> - "
"需要有效的按月或按年订阅。<br /><strong>精英</strong> - 仅终身会员专享。<br /><strong>独家</strong> -"
" 由独立交易者创建并在我们的平台上发布。这些不包含在任何会员资格中，必须与作者分开购买。"

msgid "Do I need a paid TradingView account?"
msgstr "我需要付费 TradingView 帐户吗？"

msgid ""
"No, a free TradingView account is enough to get started. However, the free "
"version has some limitations — for example, you can only have one active "
"alert and one chart with one strategy. A paid TradingView plan is "
"recommended for full functionality, especially if you plan to use "
"automation."
msgstr ""
"不，一个免费的 TradingView 帐户就足以开始。但是，免费版本有一些限制 - 例如，您只能拥有一个活动警报和一张图表以及一种策略。建议使用付费 "
"TradingView 计划以获得完整功能，特别是如果您计划使用自动化。"

msgid "What plans are available?"
msgstr "有哪些计划可供选择？"

msgid ""
"We offer three plans:<br /><strong>Monthly</strong> — perfect for trying out"
" the service, cancel anytime.<br /><strong>Yearly</strong> — best value for "
"long-term use, save significantly vs monthly.<br /><strong>Lifetime</strong>"
" — a one-time payment for permanent access to all Premium and Elite "
"strategies, plus a numbered digital membership card."
msgstr ""
"我们提供三种计划：<br /><strong>每月</strong> - 非常适合试用服务，可随时取消。<br "
"/><strong>每年</strong> - 长期使用最超值，与每月相比可节省大量费用。<br /><strong>终身</strong> - "
"一次性付款即可永久访问所有高级和精英策略，以及编号的数字会员卡。"

msgid "Can I automate my trades?"
msgstr "我可以自动化我的交易吗？"

msgid ""
"Yes. You can connect any TradingView strategy or indicator to multiple "
"crypto and forex brokers using our webhook integration. Use our Playground "
"tool to configure alert messages, connect your broker, and trades execute "
"automatically.<br /><br />An additional fee of $3 to $20/month applies per "
"connected trading account depending on the broker type."
msgstr ""
"是的。您可以使用我们的 webhook 集成将任何 TradingView 策略或指标连接到多个加密货币和外汇经纪商。使用我们的 Playground "
"工具配置警报消息、连接您的经纪商并自动执行交易。<br /><br />每个连接的交易账户每月需支付 3 至 20 "
"美元的额外费用，具体取决于经纪商类型。"

msgid "Can I trust the performance reports?"
msgstr "我可以相信绩效报告吗？"

msgid ""
"Yes. Our reports reflect the actual backtested performance of each strategy "
"over a specific time period. The longer the period covered, the more "
"reliable the results. Keep in mind that past performance does not guarantee "
"future results, but it gives you a solid basis for evaluating a strategy."
msgstr ""
"是的。我们的报告反映了每个策略在特定时间段内的实际回测表现。涵盖的时间越长，结果就越可靠。请记住，过去的表现并不能保证未来的结果，但它为您评估策略提供了坚实的基础。"

msgid "Can I change or cancel my plan?"
msgstr "我可以更改或取消我的计划吗？"

msgid ""
"Yes, you can upgrade, downgrade, or cancel at any time. When you upgrade, "
"remaining time converts into extra days on your new plan. Downgrades take "
"effect after the current billing period ends. When you cancel, you keep "
"access until the end of your current period."
msgstr ""
"是的，您可以随时升级、降级或取消。升级后，剩余时间将转换为新计划的额外天数。降级在当前计费周期结束后生效。取消后，您将保留访问权限，直到当前期限结束。"

msgid "IsAlgo Documentation | Share Your Strategy Results After Backtesting"
